white/off-white     →    near-black (#1a1a1a)
light gray          →    dark gray (#2a2a2a)
dark text           →    light text (#e5e5e5)
borders (light)     →    borders (subtle light, #333)
accent colors       →    same hue, adjusted brightness
```

**Dark Mode Surfaces:**
