```
┌─────────────────────────┐
│ Label          [badge]  │  ← Section label + time filter
│ 1,234  ↗ 12.5%         │  ← Large value + trend indicator
│ ▁▂▃▂▄▅▃▂▁▂▃▄           │  ← Sparkline chart
└─────────────────────────┘
```

