## Quick Reference Checklist

Before shipping any UI:

**Foundation:**
- [ ] Visual hierarchy is clear (can scan in 2 seconds)
- [ ] Spacing follows 4px scale consistently
- [ ] Color is semantic, not decorative (90% neutral)
- [ ] Containers have consistent padding/radius
- [ ] Typography uses defined size/weight scale

**Interaction:**
- [ ] All interactive states defined (hover, focus, active, disabled)
- [ ] Status feedback is immediate and clear
- [ ] Keyboard shortcuts surfaced where appropriate

**Overlays & Positioning:**
- [ ] Modals/popovers use backdrop blur (retain context)
- [ ] Overlays anchored to trigger element (not floating randomly)
- [ ] Viewport collision handled (flip/shift at edges)
- [ ] Animation originates from anchor point

**Data & Metrics:**
- [ ] Trend indicators show direction and magnitude
- [ ] Sparklines provide context without clutter
- [ ] Connection diagrams use curved lines, clear spacing

**Content:**
- [ ] Data is aligned and scannable
- [ ] Long content has progressive disclosure
- [ ] Feature badges/labels guide discovery
- [ ] Empty states invite action (not just "Nothing here")

**Forms & Builders:**
- [ ] Section labels are consistent (ALL CAPS or sentence case)
- [ ] Destructive actions styled in red text
- [ ] Flow nodes have clear type indicators

**Polish:**
- [ ] Decorative elements below 20% opacity
- [ ] Dark mode contrast verified (if applicable)
- [ ] Icons have consistent sizing and color treatment
- [ ] Blur tested against varied backgrounds
